Package: brfinance
Title: Simplified Access to Brazilian Financial Data
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: 
    person("João Paulo", "Barbosa", 
           email = "joao.31582129@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides programmatic access to Brazilian economic and financial data, 
             including interest rates (such as the SELIC base rate), unemployment, and other indicators
             from official sources such as the Central Bank and IBGE. The data is returned in tidy formats ready for analysis.
             tidy prontos para análise.
